= Paid Advertising Strategy

== Google Ads (Local Service Ads)

*Why:* Highest intent — people actively searching for roofing services

*Budget Recommendation:* \$2,000-5,000/month per major market

*Key Campaigns:*
+ Brand terms (Xperience Roofing)
+ Service terms (roof repair, roof replacement)
+ Emergency terms (emergency roof repair, storm damage)
+ Location terms ([City] roofers)

*Tracking:* Phone call tracking, form submissions, quote requests

== Facebook/Instagram Ads

*Why:* Awareness building, retargeting, storm response

*Budget Recommendation:* \$1,000-3,000/month

*Campaign Types:*
+ Awareness: Before/after video ads to cold audiences
+ Consideration: Educational content, free inspection offers
+ Retargeting: Website visitors, video viewers, page engagers
+ Storm Response: Rapid deployment during hail/wind events

*Targeting:*
- Homeowners in service area
- Age 35-65
- Interests: Home improvement, real estate, homeownership
- Lookalike audiences from customer list

